    "title": "Looking for Real Estate Agent at Anarock Property Consultants",
    "description": "Are you a skilled Real Estate Agent looking for your next big career move? Anarock Property Consultants in Raipur offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Anarock Property Consultants:\nAnarock Property Consultants is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Liaise with banks and NBFCs for home loan assistance to customers\n• Manage RERA documentation and compliance requirements\n• Achieve monthly and quarterly sales targets\n• Negotiate pricing, terms, and conditions on behalf of clients\n• Source and close property deals with prospective buyers and investors\n• Prepare presentations and proposals for institutional clients\n• Provide advisory services on property investment and market trends\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Property Valuation\n• Proficiency in MS Office\n• Proficiency in Property Management\n• Proficiency in Contract Management\n• Proficiency in Negotiation Skills\n• Proficiency in Due Diligence\n• Proficiency in Real Estate Law\n• Proficiency in Market Research\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Flexible working hours\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Raipur, Chhattisgarh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Anarock Property Consultants!",
